#
#  Solutions
#
#

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

a. [`f(x)=[$f] \quad\underset{x\rightarrow a}\longrightarrow\quad f(a) =  [$fa]`] 

b. [`f(x)=[$f] \quad\underset{x\rightarrow a+h}\longrightarrow\quad f(a+h) =  [$fB] (a+h) + [$fC] \quad\longrightarrow\quad [$fah] `] 

    So [`f(a+h) = [$fah] `].
    
c. [`f(a+h)-f(a) \quad\longrightarrow\quad ([$fah])-([$fa]) \quad\longrightarrow\quad [$fah] - [$fB] a - [$fC] \quad\longrightarrow\quad [$fdqNumer] `] 
  
      So [`f(a+h)-f(a) = [$fdqNumer] `].
  
d. [`\displaystyle \frac{f(a+h) - f(a)}{h} \quad\longrightarrow\quad 
\frac{[$fdqNumer]}{h} \quad\longrightarrow\quad  [$fdq] `]

    So [`\dfrac{f(a+h) - f(a)}{h} = [$fdq] `].
    
END_PGML_SOLUTION




